      "lineNumber": 250612,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まずは１回最期まで進めてみましょう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Let's try progressing to the very end once first."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250613,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「では、クリア後にまたお会いしましょう",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Well then, let's meet again after you clear it."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250614,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ぜひランスの物語を最期までクリアしてね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Please make sure to clear Rance's story until the very end."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250615,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "補足・・・ 他、何か必要なヒントがあれば追加",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Supplement... Add any other necessary hints if needed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250616,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　宝箱を気にしすぎない、キャラが増える宝箱欲しいですが、じっと我慢",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Don't worry too much about treasure chests; although you'd want chests that add new characters, just endure patiently."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250617,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　体力の回復を優先した方がいいです、うんぬん",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It's better to prioritize recovering health, and so on."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250618,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランス０１　−光を求めて−",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance 01 - In Search of Light -"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250619,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "１９８９年発売　（２０１３年リメイク版０１）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Released in 1989 (2013 Remake Version 01)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250620,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　６４０＊４００、１６色、ＰＣ９８他",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "640×400, 16 colors, PC-98 and others"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250621,
      "originalJapaneseLine": " ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250622,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "我が儘でエロ大好きな駆け出しの冒険者ランス君",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance, a selfish and lecherous fledgling adventurer"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250623,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "とその奴隷シィルちゃんの冒険です",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and his slave girl Sheila's adventure."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250624,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "大国リーザスの城下町でギルドから仕事を受けます",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They accept a job from the guild in the castle town of the great nation Leazas."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250625,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "パリス学園に在学中に行方不明になったヒカルという",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A girl named Hikaru went missing while attending Paris Academy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250626,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "女の子を見つける事",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Their task is to find that girl."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250627,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスは、城下町で情報収集",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance gathers information in the castle town."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250628,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "シィルは、学生に変装してパリス学園で情報収集",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Sheila disguises herself as a student and collects information at Paris Academy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250629,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "謎の忍者(かなみ)に命を狙われたり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They are targeted for assassination by a mysterious ninja (Kanami)..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250630,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "盗賊団をアジトに侵入して壊滅させたり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They infiltrate a bandit gang's hideout and wipe them out..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250631,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "町の女の子を襲ったり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They assault girls in town..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250632,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そうしている内にリーザス城に入れるようになり",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Meanwhile, they become able to enter Leazas Castle,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250633,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "コロシアムで優勝したり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "win the coliseum..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250634,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "墓地で幽霊退治をしたり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "exorcise ghosts in the graveyard..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250635,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "目的のヒカリは見つからないが、いろいろ目立つと",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They can't find the target Hikaru, but they start standing out in various ways,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250636,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "リーザスの王女に仕事を依頼されたり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and receive work assignments from the princess of Leazas..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250637,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "キエン屋敷で幽霊を救ったり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "rescue ghosts at the Kien mansion..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250638,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "で、もって黒幕がリア王女と判明",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and then discover that the mastermind is Princess Ria."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250639,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "逃げる王女と追いかけ…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They chase after the fleeing princess..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250640,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "忍者(かなみ)と侍女(マリス)をやっつけ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "defeat the ninja (Kanami) and the maid (Marisu)."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250641,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "最期は、リア王女のお仕置きレイプで処女を奪って",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In the end, they take Princess Ria's virginity during her punishment rape."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250642,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "めでたし、めでたし",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "And so, all is well."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250643,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "はにほー",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Haniho~"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250644,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Let's summarize setting points that will be relevant later."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250645,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "鬼畜な冒険者ランスと奴隷のシィルちゃん",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "The brutal adventurer Rance and his slave Sheila."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250646,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "事件を解決してリーザス王国のリア王女に惚れられる",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They solve the incident and get loved by Princess Ria of the Leazas Kingdom."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250647,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔王美樹、リーザス城でちょこっと出会う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Demon Lord Miki appears briefly at Leazas Castle."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250648,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "忍者かなみ、ランスを敵認識",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Ninja Kanami recognizes Rance as an enemy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250649,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "Ｒａｎｃｅ２　−反逆少女達−",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance 2 - The Rebel Girls -"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250650,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "１９９０年発売（２００９年リメイク版０２）",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Released in 1990 (2009 Remake Version 02)"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250651,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　６４０＊４００、１６色、ＰＣ９８他",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "640×400, 16 colors, PC-98 and others"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250652,
      "originalJapaneseLine": " ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": ""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250653,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "自由都市にあるカスタムという町",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "A town called Custom in the Free City."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250654,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一晩で地下に陥没した状態になってしまった",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "It collapsed underground overnight."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250655,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "４人の魔女が反乱を起こしたのだ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Four witches staged a rebellion."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250656,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ランスとシィルは、町を元に戻す為に",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Rance and Sheila, to restore the town,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250657,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "反乱を起こした４人の魔女の退治を依頼された",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "were entrusted with exterminating the four witches who rebelled."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250658,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "町のさらに地下に作られた人工迷宮を攻略",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They clear an artificial labyrinth created further underground."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250659,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ピラミッド迷宮で鏡のワープ…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mirror warp in the pyramid labyrinth..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250660,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "シィルとはぐれてしまったり…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They get separated from Sheila..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250661,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "幼体迷宮で囚われ拷問される女の子達…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Girls captured and tortured in the larva labyrinth..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250662,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "鏡のワープ仕掛け…ゴールデンハニーとの戦い…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Mirror warp mechanism... Battle with Golden Honey..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250663,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "町の女の子を襲ったりとか…",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Assaulting girls in town..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250664,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔女１(マリア)を倒し処女を奪う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Defeat Witch 1 (Maria) and take her virginity."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250665,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔女２(ミル)を倒し処女を奪う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Defeat Witch 2 (Mil) and take her virginity."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250666,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔女３(エレノア)を倒し処女を奪う",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Defeat Witch 3 (Elenoa) and take her virginity."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250667,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "最期は、魔女４(志津香)をのみという所で",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Finally, just when they are about to only defeat Witch 4 (Shizuka),"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250668,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "本当に悪いのは彼女達でなく",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "They discover that the real villains are not them,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250669,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "師匠であるラギシスという事が判明",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but their master, Ragisis."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250670,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "魔女４(志津香)を追いかけ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Chasing after Witch 4 (Shizuka),"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250671,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "過去へ飛ぼうとしていた志津香を捕まえ",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "they catch Shizuka, who was trying to jump into the past."
    }
  ]
}

